normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5037db348d6b6fa91a5b046a89ef83c255e63c7","tid":431924,"uid":101777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"好掛住細細個寫體適能個陣<br />\n一定問全班最勁一兩個做到幾多<br />\n再作個數出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時係得長跑先會認真啲<br />\n<br />\n宜家睇住自己細佬 中意打籃球<br />\n但係又係名校 狂谷成績<br />\n日日食勁多野 肉都唔生下"},{"pid":"e7260cdfd6f5d90930e9325c2b2328e3f4c26a6e","tid":431924,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先算體能差？<br />\n我依家中四 落街場連踢一個半鐘都唔會累喎</blockquote><br />\n中四已經出來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 丙朗踢一場90 分鐘都要收皮啦，踢街場唔攰明顯唔算體能好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主講果啲一下掌上壓都做唔到，去次camp 或者行下山出街拎重野都有難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be850e03c5f18aea786a5b14c5c884e0966a03c","tid":431924,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間中學大部份都係南亞裔<br />\n身形超勁<br />\n體能又掂</blockquote><br />\n屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"bf942ec732135d43699c81aef1e1c85a918015a3","tid":431924,"uid":125539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>功利d講<br />\n體能好對未來無乜幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左考紀律部隊同做pe老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定要體能好好，但起碼有個健康體態<br />\n身型好無型間幫咗你好多，又有自信健康"},{"pid":"90c62aae09c1c707c225b716b79962914a947596","tid":431924,"uid":104579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間中學大部份都係南亞裔<br />\n身形超勁<br />\n體能又掂</blockquote><br />\n自己讀垃圾學校唔